<l>maṟavaṟka mācaṟṟār kēṇmai tuṟavaṟka</l>
<l>tuṉpattuṭ ṭuppāyār naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Forget not the friendship of the faultless; forsake not</l>
<l>the bond of those who were one's strength in sorrow.</l>
